Signed-off-by: Linus Walleij <linus.walleij@linaro.org>
Tested-by: Christophe Leroy <christophe.leroy@c-s.fr>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20191128083718.39177-2-linus.walleij@linaro.org
